      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound FD3S RX-7 featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary powerplant. This chassis retains its factory sequential twin-turbo configuration, delivering a linear power band through a crisp five-speed manual gearbox. The vehicle benefits from a Torsen LSD and a lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension setup, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution remains uncompromised. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul to manage thermal loads effectively. Exterior and interior present well with minor patina consistent with age. A true driver\u2019s car with excellent compression and sharp turn-in response.",
